{"tid":1737602,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"國際陣線應該要打呢樣野","createTime":"2019-11-19T04:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T04:20:36.000Z","uid":76957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"643a57616e0034abb77715577751d7d79a4c42ba","tid":1737602,"uid":76957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:03:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_4995046?from=groupmessage&amp;fbclid=IwAR3CNQt0MWE6tgvaakIDrrqH8v29VFcHcKFVSQA-N6l-jGUY1No3R7oeYBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.thepaper.cn%2FnewsDetail_forward_4995046%3Ffrom%3Dgroupmessage%26fbclid%3DIwAR3CNQt0MWE6tgvaakIDrrqH8v29VFcHcKFVSQA-N6l-jGUY1No3R7oeYBY&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfG9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=5b59bf8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_4995046?from=groupmessage&amp;fbclid=IwAR3CNQt0MWE6tgvaakIDrrqH8v29VFcHcKFVSQA-N6l-jGUY1No3R7oeYBY</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;我们正在研究一些全国人大代表提出的有关意见和建议。&quot;</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n國際上 我地需要強烈地比西方國家知道<br />\n法治危機已經黎到<br />\n令到佢地睇實中共<br />\n推到佢地當一旦人大再釋法 會肯做制裁<br />\n要明白司法獨立係香港最重要既精神<br />\n係因為咁先可以做到金融自由港<br />\n一旦法治精神完全被破壞 一定要攬炒<br />\n一定要比國際知<br />\n<br />\nbtw 而家國際戰線係主打人道牌<br />\n其實係好 係多人留意 有民心 多支持 理應同時繼續打<br />\n但係始終<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">好現實 國家政府做事係睇利益</span></span><br />\n所以你講民主自由 除非又有六四 否則國際社會幫極有限<br />\n出師冇名之餘 又唔係真係有極大人道危機<br />\n所以話佢地知 佢地再唔發威比中共睇 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就會有經濟損失</span></span><br />\n認同既 麻煩幫手推一推"},{"pid":"fd9428bc5603632db6c9b300ba738feb12bb20ec","tid":1737602,"uid":76957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:06:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9471bf8217ad348547bc0032e5c6fce308c8dc8f","tid":1737602,"uid":76957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9729c75ccf9f85e76ba8fb307fe4634ccb82f70","tid":1737602,"uid":76957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0659d0dc16a11843606eaabf21a9e768a529eb1f","tid":1737602,"uid":76957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:08:33.000Z","msg":"要令其他政府做野<br />\n就要引發更多輿論<br />\n咁就要係國際上推呢樣野"},{"pid":"ef4c5c6736d4d25d8edb155128971c82a3131092","tid":1737602,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:20:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\n【行動】Twitter 戰線：世界各地政要火力全開！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F